high_descs: Go left and face the counter with the gray bowl.
Pick the gray bowl up from the counter.
Go left and turn to face the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the bowl in and shut the door and then open the door and pick up the bowl and shut the door.
Go left and then turn left again to face the brown shelves.
Put the bowl on the shelves.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl on a shelf.

high_descs: Walk a few feet left then turn right to face the kitchen island
Pick up the bowl from the kitchen island
Turn left and walk to the fridge
Put the bowl in the fridge then remove it
Turn left and walk around the kitchen island to the wooden shelf in the corner
Put the bowl on the middle shelf next to the coffee mug
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled bowl on the wooden shelf

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the kitchen island.
Pick up the gray bowl from the kitchen island.
Take the bowl over to the fridge that is on your left.
Place the bowl on the top shelf to chill before pulling it back out.
Turn left to move forward, hang a left once you reach the end of the kitchen island, then walk to the brown shelving that is on your right.
Place the bowl to the right of the white mug on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled mug onto a shelf.

high_descs: Move to the island across from the stove.
Pick up a bowl from the island.
Move to the left to the fridge,
Place the bowl inside and close the door, let chill for a moment before retrieving the bowl and closing the door.
Move to the wooden shelf to the left of the stove.
Place the bowl on the wooden shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl on the wooden shelf.

high_descs: Turn left, then turn right to face the kitchen island.
Pick up the bowl on the kitchen island.
Turn left to go to the fridge.
Chill the bowl in the fridge.
Turn left, then go straight, then turn left, then turn right to face the shelves at the end of the counter.
Put the bowl on the second shelf, to the left of the glass.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn left, move half way down counter, turn to right.
Facing counter, pick up large silver bowl to the right of the plate.
Turn left, move to fridge.  Turn left to face fridge.
Open fridge, place bowl on top shelf, close fridge.  Wait several seconds.  Open fridge, remove silver bowl.
Turn left, follow along counter, turn left at end of counter.  Turn right, facing counter and shelf.
Place bowl on shelf to the left, second shelf up.  Place in between bug, glass and shaker.
anns.task_desc: Move bowl in and out of fridge and place on shelf.
